{"tid":627293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉偷40元貨品　警務人員被控盜竊","createTime":"2018-04-13T00:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T00:25:30.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef7482f6e6109c298340d7ffd41540a0c362744","tid":627293,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T00:09:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180412/s00001/1523547791057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180412%2Fs00001%2F1523547791057&d=M6jJmP57NPtmAhd7TGJY2mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d6060c27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180412%2Fs00001%2F1523547791057&h=e58d4741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180412/s00001/1523547791057</a><br />\n<br />\n荃灣上月發生店鋪盜竊案，涉案54歲姓沈男警務人員，星期四（12日）正式被控一項盜竊罪。案件將於本月26日在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<del><br />\n警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。</del><br />\n<br />\n事發上月14日，荃灣青山公路398號愉景新城商場一間店鋪，保安員報案指一名男子涉嫌盜去一件價值約40元的貨品，警員接到場調查後，沈涉嫌店鋪盜竊被捕，其後案件由新界南總區重案組跟進。"},{"pid":"34cc99cd3fe6b9b8769e38ddb0865e618dd5f3fe","tid":627293,"uid":8048,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T00:10:22.000Z","msg":"最大犯罪集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2aee6aff2df788d8ed907912c711b6b6965d22","tid":627293,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T00:10:32.000Z","msg":"同法官求情一日最衰都係佔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b05719faffa80bba75d3420df9dfecd000d4051","tid":627293,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T00:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk